1
00:00:08,375 --> 00:00:15,548
I've seen death. I've seen my friends,
my men, being killed.

2
00:00:15,549 --> 00:00:22,179
And this is... It doesn't take
too many days of that...

3
5
00:00:29,438 --> 00:00:34,734
We didn't have clothes. If you built
a fire, something would shoot at you.

4
00:00:34,735 --> 00:00:38,446
Everywhere you look,
you would see dead people.

5
00:00:38,447 --> 00:00:41,783
A dead soldier there, here.
Ours, theirs.

6
00:00:41,784 --> 00:00:47,120
Then civilians, besides...
Dead animals.

7
00:00:47,122 --> 00:00:49,665
So death was all over.

8
00:00:49,666 --> 00:00:55,171
You don't have a chance,
when your friends go down...

9
00:00:55,172 --> 00:01:00,051
...to really take care of them
as you might.

10
00:01:00,052 --> 00:01:06,422
And especially if you're under attack,
moving or whatever, and...

11
00:01:07,434 --> 00:01:11,062
I withstood it well...

12
00:01:11,063 --> 00:01:16,818
...but I had a lot of trouble
in later life...

13
00:01:16,819 --> 00:01:22,824
...because those events
would come back...

14
00:01:22,825 --> 00:01:26,556
...and you never forget them.

